---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import experience from '../content/experience/_ordered.json';

// ‚úÖ Local portrait as a real asset (no CLS, optimized)
import portrait from '../assets/personal.jpg';

const fmtMY = (iso) =>
  iso ? new Date(iso).toLocaleString('en-US', { month: 'short', year: 'numeric' }) : '';

const cardBase = 'rounded-2xl bg-white border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden shadow-sm transition-all duration-300';
const card = `${cardBase} hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 p-5`;
---

<Layout
  title="About ‚Äî Dimitrios Ntempos"
  description="Dimitri (Dimitrios Ntempos) ‚Äî Technical Product Manager and Builder connecting systems, data, and people."
>
  <!-- Opportunistic prefetch for likely next pages -->
  <link rel="prefetch" href="/projects" />
  <link rel="prefetch" href="/writing" />

  <article>
    <!-- Intro -->
    <section class="mb-4" aria-labelledby="about">
      <div class="flex flex-col-reverse md:flex-row items-center md:items-start gap-8">
        <!-- Text -->
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h1 id="about" class="text-3xl font-bold mb-1 text-gray-900">More about me</h1>
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-semibold text-lg mb-3">
            Driven by curiosity ‚Äî blending Economics, Informatics, and human systems.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4 max-w-2xl">
            I‚Äôve always been drawn to understanding how things work, in both science and systems. My
            curiosity started with <strong>üß™Chemistry</strong>, where I first learned how physical
            elements interact, then moved to <strong>üè¶Economics</strong>, where I studied how modern
            society is fueled and markets behave, and finally to <strong>üíªInformatics</strong>, where
            I learned how technology connects it all together in a digital universe.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Portrait (local Image) -->
        <div data-no-invert class="flex-shrink-0">
          <Image
            src={portrait}
            alt="Portrait of Dimitrios Ntempos"
            width={260}
            height={260}
            loading="eager"
            fetchpriority="high"
            decoding="async"
            class="w-52 h-52 md:w-60 md:h-60 rounded-full object-cover border-4 border-white shadow-md"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Values -->
    <section class="mb-4" aria-labelledby="values">
      <h2 id="values" class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Values</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
        After working with cross-functional and international teams, I‚Äôve come to believe that people and
        culture shape every outcome. Finding the right mix of the elements below can make any organization
        thrive.
      </p>
      <div class="grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
        <div class={card}>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Simplicity</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">
            Clear systems lead to clear thinking ‚Äî build less, mean more.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class={card}>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Transparency</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">
            Open context drives better alignment and trust.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class={card}>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Community</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">
            Diverse perspectives create stronger products and teams.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class={card}>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Craftsmanship</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">
            Take ownership, responsibility, and aim for quality.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Craftsmanship -->
    <section class="mb-4" aria-labelledby="professional">
      <h2 id="professional" class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Craftsmanship</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
        I‚Äôve spent the past decade in product management, helping tech startups and early-stage scaleups to design and launch better systems, automate workflows, and turn insights into impact. I enjoy projects that live at the intersection of product, data, and operations.
      </p>

      <div class="grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div class={card}>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Turning data into decisions</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">
            Building pipelines to harvest data that inform strategy.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="text-xs bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 px-2 py-1 rounded-md font-medium">#SQL</span>
            <span class="text-xs bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 px-2 py-1 rounded-md font-medium">#Plotly</span>
            <span class="text-xs bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 px-2 py-1 rounded-md font-medium">#Sheets</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class={card}>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Systems &amp; integrations</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">
            Connecting services seamlessly across platforms.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="text-xs bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 px-2 py-1 rounded-md font-medium">#APIs</span>
            <span class="text-xs bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 px-2 py-1 rounded-md font-medium">#Webhooks</span>
            <span class="text-xs bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 px-2 py-1 rounded-md font-medium">#Sockets</span>
            <span class="text-xs bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 px-2 py-1 rounded-md font-medium">#SDK</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class={card}>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Documentation that guides</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">
            Writing readable docs that keep teams aligned.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="text-xs bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 px-2 py-1 rounded-md font-medium">#Notion</span>
            <span class="text-xs bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 px-2 py-1 rounded-md font-medium">#Jira</span>
            <span class="text-xs bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 px-2 py-1 rounded-md font-medium">#Aha</span>
            <span class="text-xs bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 px-2 py-1 rounded-md font-medium">#Docs</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class={card}>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Automation and AI</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">
            Pair automation with clear guidance to scale outcomes.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="text-xs bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 px-2 py-1 rounded-md font-medium">#OpenAI</span>
            <span class="text-xs bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 px-2 py-1 rounded-md font-medium">#Python</span>
            <span class="text-xs bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 px-2 py-1 rounded-md font-medium">#Copilot</span>
            <span class="text-xs bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 px-2 py-1 rounded-md font-medium">#AppScript</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class={card}>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Advocating for UX</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">
            Sketching wireframes and user flows a lot. User centered design principles. Launching with empathy.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="text-xs bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 px-2 py-1 rounded-md font-medium">#Notion</span>
            <span class="text-xs bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 px-2 py-1 rounded-md font-medium">#Jira</span>
            <span class="text-xs bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 px-2 py-1 rounded-md font-medium">#Aha</span>
            <span class="text-xs bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 px-2 py-1 rounded-md font-medium">#Docs</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class={card}>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Agile minded and team-player</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">
            People over processes for the win.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="text-xs bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 px-2 py-1 rounded-md font-medium">#Notion</span>
            <span class="text-xs bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 px-2 py-1 rounded-md font-medium">#Jira</span>
            <span class="text-xs bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 px-2 py-1 rounded-md font-medium">#Aha</span>
            <span class="text-xs bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 px-2 py-1 rounded-md font-medium">#Docs</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Experience -->
    <section class="mb-4" aria-labelledby="experience">
      <h2 id="experience" class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Experience</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
        I‚Äôve spent the past decade in product management as an independent contractor who helps tech startups and early-stage scaleups to design and launch better systems,
        automate workflows, and turn insights into impact. I enjoy projects that live at the intersection of product, data, and operations.
      </p>

      <ul class="grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2">
        {experience.map((item, i) => (
          <li key={(item.role || item.company) + i} class={card}>
            <!-- Title + Current badge -->
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-gray-900">{item.role || '‚Äî'}</h3>
              {item.current && (
                <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wide bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700 border border-emerald-200 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">
                  Current
                </span>
              )}
            </div>

            <!-- Company + Date -->
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-600 mt-1">
              <span class="font-semibold text-gray-700">{item.company}</span>
              {item.start && <span>{' ‚Ä¢ '}{fmtMY(item.start)}</span>}
              {item.location && <span>{' ‚Ä¢ '}{item.location}</span>}
            </p>

            <!-- Tags -->
            {item.tags?.length > 0 && (
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-3">
                {item.tags.map((tag) => (
                  <span class="text-xs bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 px-2 py-1 rounded-md font-medium">#{tag}</span>
                ))}
              </div>
            )}

            <!-- Summary -->
            {item.description && (
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-3 whitespace-pre-line">{item.description}</p>
            )}
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>

      <div class="mt-6 flex justify-end">
        <a
          href="/projects"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-2.5 rounded-full text-sm font-medium
                 bg-indigo-600 text-white hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-colors
                 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-indigo-400"
        >
          Request Full Resume ‚Üí
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>
